## Quick commands

```powershell
mc open {{DISTRO}}     # open VS Code Remote-WSL
mc dev {{DISTRO}}      # npm run dev inside the distro
mc shell {{DISTRO}}    # interactive shell
mc auth status {{DISTRO}}   # check pac/az auth
mc logout {{DISTRO}}   # logout at end of day
```

For deploy:

```powershell
$env:PP_SOLUTION = '{{SOLUTION}}'
mc deploy {{DISTRO}}
```

